36
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,810
Maafkan aku tolong minggirlah.

37
00:02:14,810 --> 00:02:17,830
Sekarang kau mahir berpura-pura.
Berhenti pamer dan pergi saja.

38
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:19,730
Kubilang pergi!

39
00:02:19,730 --> 00:02:22,420
- Kembali!
- Biarkan dia masuk!

40
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:25,340
- Kau mau kemana?
- Biarkan aku masuk.

41
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:27,200
Hei, lepaskan!

42
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,310
Kau tak boleh masuk!

43
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:31,590
Kau pikir apa yang kau lakukan?

44
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:36,570
Anggota Dewan.

45
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,420
Tenanglah.

46
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:54,490
Sang Pil, itu disana.

47
00:02:54,490 --> 00:02:58,090
Minggir. Minggir. Minggir

